*Advokat* je u sudnici zastupao svojeg klijenta. (The lawyer represented his client in the courtroom.)

Sudija je zatražio da *advokat* iznese svoj argument. (The judge requested for the lawyer to present his argument.)

*Advokat* je poslao punomoć za zastupanje. (The lawyer sent a power of attorney for representation.)

Nakon dugog sudskog postupka, *advokat* je za svojeg klijenta uspeo da dobije sudsku odluku. (After a long legal process, the lawyer managed to get a court decision for his client.)

*Advokat* je pružio svoje savete svojoj novoj klijentici. (The lawyer gave his advice to his new client.)